    "body" : "<p>you can find info in this related question: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/310720/get-source-jar-files-attached-to-eclipse-for-maven-managed-dependencies\">Get source jar files attached to Eclipse for Maven-managed dependencies</a>\n<br />\nif you use the eclipse maven plugin then use 'mvn eclipse:eclipse -DdownloadSources=true'</p>\n"
