    "body" : "<p>In eclipse - click on the project then:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lfnnK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lfnnK.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a>.</p>\n"
