    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you know the <strong>groupId</strong> and <strong>aritifactId</strong>,you can generate download url like this.</p>\n<pre><code>  &lt;dependency&gt;\n      &lt;groupId&gt;ch.qos.logback&lt;/groupId&gt;\n      &lt;artifactId&gt;logback-classic&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n      &lt;version&gt;1.2.3&lt;/version&gt;\n  &lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"http://central.maven.org/maven2/ch/qos/logback/logback-classic/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://central.maven.org/maven2/ch/qos/logback/logback-classic/</a></p>\n<p>and you will get a page like this, chose the version you need,just enjoy it!\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/pkLAC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/pkLAC.jpg\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/narOO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/narOO.jpg\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
