    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For debugging you can also use a \"Java Decompiler\" such as: JAD and decompile source on the fly (although the generated source is never the same as the original).  Then install JAD as a plugin in Eclipse or your favorite IDE.</p>\n"
