    "answer_id" : 58619970,
    "question_id" : 2059431,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In IntelliJ IDEA you can download artifact sources automatically while importing by switching on Automatically download Sources option:</p>\n\n<p><code>Settings</code> →  <code>Build, Execution, Deployment</code> → <code>Build Tools</code> → <code>Maven</code> → <code>Importing</code></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lmfUn.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lmfUn.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 8231410,
      "reputation" : 193,
