    "question_id" : 2059431,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you want find the source jar file for any of the artifact manually, go to maven repository location for the particular artifact and in Files click on 'view All'. You can find source jar file.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2278572,
